<img src="/content/dam/news-events/news/2019/01/angela-de-montigny-2.jpg" alt="Angela DeMontigny"/>




					 
						<div class="caption richtextContent">
	<p>Angela DeMontigny in a School of Fashion studio. Photo credit: Jenna Marie Wakani.</p>
</div>
						    
					
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
